  "title": "Sales Specialist (Materials Science)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Our client is a local leading player in Scientific devices provider sector. Due to their current expansion plan, they are looking for a Product Specialist to join their Sales Team, in hopes of developing the current high performing team. They are located in the South area – easily accessible.</strong></p><p><strong>Duties of Product Specialist:</strong></p><ul><li>Executing effective sales and marketing activities to achieve business objectives.</li><li>Managing business development initiatives and strategically positioning products and services.</li><li>Liaising with suppliers and customers in a satisfactory manner, addressing inquiries and opportunities.</li><li>Conducting market analysis to identify opportunities and enhance product positioning.</li><li>Undertaking any additional responsibilities as assigned</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Degree in Chemistry related disciplines</li><li>1 - 2 years experience in related field</li><li><strong>Entry level are welcomed to apply. Training provided</strong></li></ul><p>Interested candidates who wish to apply for the advertised position, please click <strong>APPLY NOW</strong> or email an updated copy of your resume/cv.</p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidate will be notified.</p><ul><li><strong>Email Address: jobs@recruitpedia.sg</strong></li><li>EA License No: 19C9682</li><li>EA Personnel No: R2198636</li><li>EA Personnel Name: Oh Puey Xin</li></ul>",
